                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-8">
                                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                                            <i
                                                class="bi bi-quote quote-icon"
                                            ></i>
                                            <p class="testimonial-text">
                                                "As someone transitioning
                                                careers, the UX Design course
                                                gave me the confidence and
                                                skills I needed. The portfolio
                                                projects were instrumental in
